### рҹ“Ҡ 3. `ZippyCoin-Network-Monitor` вҖ” Node Status Dashboard
**Path:** `S:\Projects\ZippyCoin-Network-Monitor`
**Remote:** `https://github.com/GoZippy/zippycoin-network-monitor.git`
**Branch:** `master` | **Version:** 1.0.0

**Purpose:** Real-time dashboard that polls all ZippyCoin node types (validator, full node, edge node) and displays block height, peer count, validator participation, and node health.

**Tech Stack:** TypeScript В· Node.js В· Express В· WebSockets

**Configuration:** `.env` file at project root. Set `RPC_URL_VALIDATOR`, `RPC_URL_FULLNODE`, `RPC_URL_EDGE` to match your cluster.

**Commands:**
```bash
npm run dev        # Development with hot reload
npm run build      # TypeScript compile -> dist/
npm start          # Run compiled server (dist/server.js)
```

**Current Status:** вң… RUNNING continuously (100+ hours uptime). Polling live nodes.

**Open TODOs:**
- [ ] Add block explorer view
- [ ] Expand edge node GPU/compute metrics
- [ ] Integrate ZippyMesh router service stats
- [ ] Add live `zippy_getTrustScore` panels

