### рҹӨ– 5. `ZippyMesh_LLM_Router` вҖ” AI LLM Routing + P2P Mesh
**Path:** `K:\Projects\ZippyMesh_LLM_Router`
**Remote:** `https://github.com/BookingBill/ZippyMesh_LLM_Router.git`
**Branch:** `dev_alpha` | **Version:** 1.6.0

**Purpose:** OpenAI-compatible smart AI routing gateway. Routes requests across multiple LLM providers with fallback logic, context compression, guardrails, and an optional P2P mesh mode via a Rust sidecar (libp2p).

**Connection Modes:**
| Mode | Target | Auth |
|------|--------|------|
| Local | `127.0.0.1:20128` | API Key / None |
| LAN | `<LAN-IP>:20128` | API Key |
| Internet | `<Public-IP>:20128` | JWT / API Key |
| ZippyMesh P2P | Model prefix `p2p/<model>` | Blockchain wallet identity |

**Tech Stack:** Node.js В· Express В· SSE В· Rust (sidecar) В· libp2p В· Gossipsub В· mDNS

**OpenAI-Compatible Endpoints:**
- `POST /v1/chat/completions`
- `POST /v1/messages` (Anthropic compat)
- `GET /api/api/sidecar/health`

**Supported Providers:** OpenAI В· Anthropic В· Gemini В· Ollama В· Kiro В· ZippyMesh P2P

**Security Features:**
- Guardrails: `src/utils/guardrails.js` (PII detection + keyword filtering)
- Transport: Noise protocol encryption via libp2p
- Identity: Ed25519 + blockchain wallet signing

**Configuration:** `.env` / `.env.example` at project root. See `docs/CONNECTIVITY.md`.

**Current Status:** вң… Active development. Guardrails live. P2P sidecar mocked for now (real inference TBD).

**Open TODOs:**
- [ ] Full P2P inference (real GPU delegation via sidecar)
- [ ] Node operator payment settlement (ZippyCoin ZPC tokens)
- [ ] Rate limiting per wallet address
- [ ] Network Explorer UI integration

