### вҡЎ 6. `ZippyFlux` вҖ” AI Agent Orchestration Platform
**Path:** `K:\Projects\ZippyFlux`
**Remote:** `https://github.com/GoZippy/ZippyFlux.git`
**Branch:** `main`

**Purpose:** Full AGI agent orchestration platform. Manages long-running agents, task graphs, tool execution, and multi-LLM routing. Built in Rust (core engine) + TypeScript (console UI + API).

**Architecture:**
- `core/` вҖ” Rust orchestration engine
  - `core/src/llm/` вҖ” LLM adapters: Claude, OpenAI (CLI), OpenAI HTTP вң… NEW, Gemini, Ollama
  - `core/src/llm/openai_http.rs` вҖ” HTTP-based adapter for custom base URLs (e.g. ZippyMesh LLM Router)
- `api/` вҖ” REST API layer (TypeScript)
- `console/` вҖ” Web console UI (React/Next.js)
- `tools/` вҖ” Agent tool registry

**Key Integration:** `HttpOpenAiAdapter` can point to `ZippyMesh_LLM_Router` to route agent inference through the mesh вҖ” enabling cryptocurrency-settlement-based AI compute.

**How to connect ZippyFlux вҶ’ ZippyMesh:**
```rust
let adapter = HttpOpenAiAdapter::new(
    "your-api-key".to_string(),
    Some("http://localhost:20128/v1".to_string())
);
```

**Current Status:** вң… Active dev. Core orchestrator and console UI functional. HTTP adapter added 2026-02-26.

**Open TODOs:**
- [ ] Wire `HttpOpenAiAdapter` into agent runner config
- [ ] Add streaming support to HTTP adapter
- [ ] ZippyCoin ZPC payment hooks for agent compute billing

