## 6. How to Update This Document

Update this file when any of the following occur:

- **New project added:** Add a row to the Summary Table (Section 1) and a new deep dive section
- **Version bump:** Update version in the Summary Table, Protocol Registry, and the relevant deep dive
- **Feature ships:** Update the Status emoji and move the item from Open TODOs to a completion note
- **New service goes live:** Add to Active Services table (Section 5)
- **New integration:** Update the architecture diagram (Section 3)
- **Git remote changes:** Update the Summary Table and deep dive

**Suggested filename for this file:** `ECOSYSTEM_CONTEXT.md`
**Suggested locations:**
- `S:\Projects\zippycoin-core\ECOSYSTEM_CONTEXT.md` (tracked in core repo)
- `S:\Projects\ZippyCoin\ECOSYSTEM_CONTEXT.md` (mirrored in archive repo for agents)
